      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, making it a dependable choice for its next owner. The exterior retains a strong finish with only minor rock chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper. Inside, the cabin is clean and free of odors, though there is some light wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, it runs smoothly with no known issues, and all service records are available for review. It\u2019s a solid, reliable car that has many miles left to offer.",
