      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project or a budget-friendly find? This car is in poor condition and ready for a dedicated owner who can give it the TLC it needs! While it requires significant work to return to its former glory, it offers a fantastic opportunity for a mechanic or hobbyist looking for a diamond in the rough.",
