    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is being sold as a reliable but well-used option. The exterior shows visible wear, including several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading in the paint finish. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it will likely require some upcoming maintenance and minor repairs to reach peak performance. The interior is intact but shows clear signs of age, such as seat wear and some staining on the carpet. It\u2019s a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle at a lower price point who doesn't mind a bit of character and some DIY projects.",
      "price": 20000.0,
