    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained in showroom condition and meeting the most rigorous standards of aesthetic and mechanical excellence. This specimen represents a rare opportunity to acquire a motorcar of pristine caliber, characterized by an impeccable exterior finish and a flawless interior environment. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this vehicle stands as a testament to superior care and uncompromising quality.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
